{"tid":272304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］又想換枕頭","createTime":"2017-06-05T17:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T09:48:47.000Z","uid":83763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"079aec841347a9bfc6c9fb2f6a7f4c5c735ca99f","tid":272304,"uid":83763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:15:53.000Z","msg":"話說兩年前隻貓係個枕頭度柯咗督尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n令我遺棄咗訓咗8年嘅枕頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直到今時今日<br />\n都依然訓得唔好<br />\n我一直係度尋找一個舒適 安穩嘅枕頭<br />\n換過幾次枕頭<br />\n而加訓緊 仙奴max 竹碳枕 <br />\n都硬係覺得個枕頭頂住個腦/條頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽講樹葉枕/唔知乜殼枕冇回彈力<br />\n訓教果時唔會同條頸鬥力<br />\n話會訓得好啲 有冇巴絲訓緊？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以分享下自己訓過最舒服嘅枕頭？"},{"pid":"b9d6b20292e9cc5f7afd1a69d7ea836a5022c3b8","tid":272304,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:16:56.000Z","msg":"未搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34e54c53be3150ba903c8d3bd0a73c837d8f751","tid":272304,"uid":106018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:28:41.000Z","msg":"男朋友隻手囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1253dcfcdf601cb9909508c3bd89b5a47a61b3b3","tid":272304,"uid":35224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"咩樹葉／竹炭／纖維／羽絨／珍珠枕 好多都托唔到條頸<br />\n一係太硬頂住個後腦 一係走晒位托唔到條頸(如果你打側訓 膊又横 床又硬就仲慘)<br />\n揀枕頭要睇你睡姿 膊橫唔橫 張床既軟硬度 同埋你有無訓開弧形枕定普通既枕頭 <br />\nxxxxmax啲枕頭回彈唔好 質料又焗 開冷氣訓又變硬 早啲買過個喇 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64315cfa9ae24d2c9c622150d7bfe7bf2315191","tid":272304,"uid":83763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T18:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男朋友隻手囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj